import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.subtract(x1, x0)
    v1 = jnp.sin(x1)
    v2 = jnp.minimum(v0, v1)
    v3 = jnp.minimum(x1, v1)
    v4 = jnp.minimum(x1, v0)
